{"timestamp": "2025-12-04 10:53:24.665209", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission complete.\n\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): leaf_router_0_1\n- Root cause: bgp_blackhole_route_leak\n\nSummary:\nA misconfigured static blackhole route 10.0.1.0/30 on leaf_router_0_1 was advertised via BGP (network 10.0.1.0/30), creating a more-specific route leak. This drew traffic for 10.0.1.1–10.0.1.3 to leaf_router_0_1 where it was dropped, breaking pc_0_1 connectivity and end-to-end reachability.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 1897, "output_tokens": 135, "total_tokens": 2032, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1792}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
